The kind of reporting we do is essential to democracy, but it is not easy, cheap, or profitable. The Intercept is an independent nonprofit news outlet. We don’t have ads, so we depend on our members — 35,000 and counting — to help us hold the powerful to account. Joining is simple and doesn’t need to cost a lot: You can become a sustaining member for as little as $3 or $5 a month. That’s all it takes to support the journalism you rely on.</span><a class="InlineDonationPromo-link InlineDonationPromo-link--en" href="https://join.theintercept.com/donate/now?referrer_post_id=290512&amp;source=web_intercept_in-article-long-2020-03-09" rel="noopener" target="_blank" data-reactid="218"><span data-reactid="219">Become&nbsp;a&nbsp;Member&nbsp;</span><span class="Icon Icon--Arrow_02_Right icon-TI_Arrow_02_Right" data-reactid="220"></span></a></div></div></div></div><div class="Post-contact Post-contact--1" data-reactid="221"><h4 class="Post-contact-header" data-reactid="222"><!-- react-text: 223 -->Contact the author<!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="224">:</span></h4><div class="Post-contact-author" data-reactid="225"><a class="" href="/staff/intercepted/" data-reactid="226"><img class="Post-contact-author-image" src="https://theintercept.imgix.net/wp-uploads/sites/1/2018/02/intercepted-1518820577.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;q=90" data-reactid="227"/></a><p class="Post-contact-details" data-reactid="228"><a class="Post-contact-link Post-contact-link--name" href="/staff/intercepted/" data-reactid="229">Intercepted</a><a class="Post-contact-link" href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#02726d66616371767142766a676b6c766770616772762c616d6f" data-reactid="230"><span class="Icon Icon--Envelope icon-TI_Envelope" data-reactid="231"></span><!-- react-text: 232 --><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="b4c4dbd0d7d5c7c0c7f4">[email&#160;protected]</span>​theintercept.com<!-- /react-text --></a></p></div></div><!-- react-empty: 233 --><!-- react-empty: 234 --><div class="Post-latest